.TH XIL\-MIGRATE "1" "2026\-04\-24" "xil\-pipeline 0.1.8" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xil\-migrate
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xil\-migrate
[-h] [--episode TAG] [--tag TAG] [--show SHOW] [--old PATH] [--new PATH] [--stems DIR] [--orig-prefix ORIG_PREFIX] [--dry-run] [--strict] [--quiet]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Migrate episode stems from an old parsed JSON to a revised one. Copies unchanged stems to their new seq\-numbered filenames; reports what still needs TTS/SFX generation. Run XILP002 afterwards to fill the gaps.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-episode\fR \fI\,TAG\/\fR
Episode tag (e.g. S02E03); derives \-\-old, \-\-new, and \-\-stems paths
automatically

.TP
\fB\-\-tag\fR \fI\,TAG\/\fR
Raw tag for non\-episodic content (e.g. V01C03, D01); same as \-\-episode but
skips format validation

.TP
\fB\-\-show\fR \fI\,SHOW\/\fR
Show name override (default: from project.json)

.TP
\fB\-\-old\fR \fI\,PATH\/\fR
Old parsed JSON (overrides \-\-episode)

.TP
\fB\-\-new\fR \fI\,PATH\/\fR
New parsed JSON (overrides \-\-episode)

.TP
\fB\-\-stems\fR \fI\,DIR\/\fR
Stems directory (overrides \-\-episode)

.TP
\fB\-\-orig\-prefix\fR \fI\,ORIG_PREFIX\/\fR
Filename prefix for the old parsed JSON (default: orig_)

.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show plan without copying any files

.TP
\fB\-\-strict\fR
Exact text match only. Default is fuzzy: ignores em\-dash/ellipsis variants so
punctuation\-only edits don't force unnecessary regen.

.TP
\fB\-\-quiet\fR
Print only the summary, not per\-stem details

